```
Reason:
The fix introduces a conditional check to ensure that the hop limit from the RA is only set if it is higher than the current hop limit of the interface. This prevents lower hop limits from overriding higher ones, thus mitigating the risk of parameter spoofing and ensuring that legitimate packets are not dropped due to a maliciously low hop limit.

